	        	<p class="lead"><strong>Application deadline:</strong> Wednesday 11 August 2021</p>
			<p>Admission to this programme will close once the programme is full. Applicants should apply as early as possible to be eligible for certain scholarships and for international visa purposes, and to ensure their application is submitted before the programme is full.</p> 
			<p>To apply, you must provide the following:</p> 
			<ul>
				<li>CV</li> 
				<li>personal statement explaining why you have chosen the programme, why this subject is important to you and why you have applied to study at the University of St Andrews in particular (500 words)</li> 
				<li>one original signed academic reference</li> 
				<li>academic transcripts and degree certificates</li> 
				<li><a href="#">evidence of English language proficiency</a> (required if English is not your first language).</li> 
			</ul>
			<p>A sample of academic writing is not required for this programme.</p> 
